{
  "stem": "13213.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were defending themselves against the Ukrainian bandits that tried to kill them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was a fight between Ukrainians and the Polish at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I presume that the Germans have equipped them both with arms so they should kill each other and not to touch them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my brother Chaim said-- we had a meeting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Always we used to meet at night for dividing the food between us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Chaim-- my brother Chaim, Yakov, and Yitshak and myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Shabtai was already at that time killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he decided he would go into the town of Huta Stepanska, find out if these people could help us maybe, and we could maybe hide there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He went in there and he found out that yeah, it's true, there are some Jews there and they don't touch them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we could stay with them there or work for some of the Polish families.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the next night, we packed up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And about one o'clock in the morning we left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it was only about 20 kilometers away from the village of Male Werbcze.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we arrived early in the morning to this Polish enclave, Huta Stepanska.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The Polish police met us there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they got all nervous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They thought that we were Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they took my brother Chaim.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they beat him up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They said he was a spy and he was giving information to the Ukrainian bandits.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were begging.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We said, we're Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They didn't believe us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they took us to a house somewhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It looked like a police station.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said we've got to kill you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We've got to shoot you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my brothers were saying, why would you want to kill us?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We-- we are Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He says, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
